Package: msgtools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Developing Diagnostic Messages
Description: A number utilities for developing and maintaining error, warning, and other messages in R packages, including checking for consistency across messages, spell-checking messages, and building message translations into various languages for purposes of localization.
